text: The Wings of Eagles is a 1957 American drama movie directed by John Ford and starring John Wayne, Dan Dailey, Maureen O'Hara, Ward Bond, Ken Curtis, Edmund Lowe, Kenneth Tobey, Henry O'Neill. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1957 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:MGM movies Category:Movies directed by John Ford
title: The Wings of Eagles
